# Student Details SQL Analysis

This project contains a dataset of Indian students along with SQL queries used to extract meaningful insights related to payments, courses, and student behavior.

## ðŸ“Œ Project Overview
The goal of this project is to analyze student data using SQL and practice:
- Basic SQL operations
- Data filtering
- Sorting & limiting
- Aggregate functions (SUM, AVG, MIN, MAX, COUNT)
- Pattern matching (LIKE)
- Conditional filters (IN, BETWEEN)

## ðŸ“‚ Dataset
The dataset includes:
- Student Name  
- Course Name  
- Payment Date  
- Payment Status  
- State  
- Price  
- Payment ID  

Dataset file: `Indian_Students_Data.csv`  
SQL code file: `student_details_command.sql`

